  "displayField": "ALERT_TYPE",
  "description": "&lt;span style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;This view layer contains forest service road safety information including road closures, warnings and bulletins within the Chilliwack and Sea to Sky Natural Resource Districts.&nbsp; Please be aware that a road is closed for safety or environmental reasons.&nbsp; These closures are usually temporary in nature, so check back regularly for updated information.&nbsp; Be advised that there may be instances where an event on a road or bridge has not yet been identified. People using Forest Service Roads should do so with caution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;Please read the ,&nbsp;&lt;a href=\"https://www.bclaws.ca/EPLibraries/bclaws_new/document/ID/freeside/70_2004\" style=\"color:rgb(0, 121, 193); text-decoration-line:none; font-family:inherit;\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;Road Use Regulations&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;and&nbsp;&lt;a href=\"https://www.bcforestsafe.org/files/tk_pdfs/gde_resrd.pdf\" style=\"color:rgb(0, 121, 193); text-decoration-line:none; font-family:inherit;\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;Resource Road User Safety Guide Brochure&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;before travelling on Forest Service Roads.&lt;/div&gt;",
